                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="a1"> <locus target="#3r">Fol. 3r</locus>: Exhortation to the brethren, incomplete. <q xml:lang="gez"> Fol. 3r: ኦአንትሙ፡ ማህበረ፡ ሐዋርያት፡ ኩኑ፡ ብሩካነ፡ ወንጹሃነ፡ ለዓም፡ ሞገሥወሰላም፡ ይኵንክሙ። እግዚአብሔር፡ ለዓም፡ አሜን። አነገብርክሙ፡ ወል፡</q>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           Crudely written, unfinished.
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a2">
                           <locus target="#4v">Fol. 4v</locus>: Ownership note. <q xml:lang="gez"> Fol. 4v: ዝመጽሐፈ፡ ቅዳሴ፡ ዘራስ፡ ስብሐት፡ ዘሠረቆ፡ ወዘፈሐቆ፡ በሥልጣነ፡ ጴጥሮስ፡ {ወጳውሎስ፡} በ፲ወ፪ሐዋርያት፡ በ፸ወ፪አርድእት፡ በ፫፻፲ወ፰ርቱዓነ፡ ሃይማኖት፡ ውጉዘ፡ ለይን [sic]።</q>
                           <q xml:lang="en"> [Fol. 4v]: This is a Missal of ras Sǝbḥat. He who stole it or erased (its text) shall be excommunicated by the authority of Peter and Paul, of the twelve apostles, of the seventy two disciples, of the three hundred and eighteen Orthodox (Fathers).</q>
                           
                        </item>
